| # | File:line | Module | Function | Comment |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `mc_att_control/mc_att_control.hpp:102` | `mc_att_control` | `Run()` checks `:227` | **Primary consumer** — converts `q_d` into a desired body rate via the quaternion attitude controller |
